Chad L. Valerio
Portfolio Manager & Managing Director
 Back


Chad L. Valerio shares portfolio management responsibilities for stressed and distressed investments. Mr. Valerio previously worked at BlueMountain Capital Management as a portfolio manager in the firm’s Distressed and Special Situations group. In that role, he managed distressed investments across a range of industries and served on multiple restructuring committees. Prior to BlueMountain, Mr. Valerio worked in Deutsche Bank’s U.S. Distressed Products group, most recently as the Head of Trading and prior to that as a research analyst. In addition, he has served on numerous private and public company Boards, including those of Overseas Shipholding Group, Inc. and International Seaways, Inc. Mr. Valerio earned a B.S.B.A., magna cum laude, from Georgetown University.





 









